Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601

Class UasDatalinkMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.UasDatalinkMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMisbMessage, INestedKlvValue
    public class UasDatalinkMessage
extends Object
implements IMisbMessage
    UAS Datalink Local Set message packet as defined by ST 0601.

    For guidance on which items are mandatory to include in ST 0601 messages, refer to ST 0902 for a list of the minimum set of UAS Datalink LS metadata items.
